/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/beltrami-pressure-analytical.md:18:3. **Beltrami = eigenfunction of Stokes operator:** curl(curl u) = -Delta u = lambda^2 u, so Delta u = -lambda^2 u.
