/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/chebyshev-sharpness-constant-field-extremizer.md:44:Critical threshold: the Chebyshev extremizer f = c * 1_A has ||f||_{L^2} = S^{5/3}/lambda^{2/3}. When E < S^{5/3}/lambda^{2/3}, the L^2 constraint is active and improves the bound. But the improvement is always a constant factor. **[VERIFIED]**
