/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/yang-mills/cao-nissim-sheffield-area-law-extension.md:2:topic: Cao-Nissim-Sheffield area law extension — threshold doubled to β < 1/24
