/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/quadratic-gravity-fakeon/causal-order-fakeon-interpretation.md:55:The tree-level Wheeler prescription extends to Anselmi's full loop-level fakeon prescription at every order. At loop level, G_Wheeler ≠ G_fakeon: naive use of Wheeler propagator in loops violates renormalizability, unitarity, and stability (Anselmi 2020, due to coexistence of ±iε). Anselmi's correct procedure (JHEP 11(2021)030): (1) compute loops with standard Feynman iε for all propagators; (2) apply spectral optical theorem to decompose into threshold contributions; (3) drop all thresholds involving fakeon frequencies; (4) remaining amplitude satisfies unitarity. Proven for arbitrary diagram topology by induction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/quadratic-gravity-fakeon/causal-order-fakeon-interpretation.md:57:**CFT's conjecture:** Dropping fakeon thresholds corresponds to the causal order forbidding the ghost from materializing at any loop order. The SJ construction, extended to interacting fields on causal sets, should reproduce this threshold-dropping procedure.
