/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/quadratic-gravity-fakeon/causal-order-fakeon-interpretation.md:122:The problem is well-posed: threshold-dropping has clear physical meaning (prevent ghosts from going on-shell), and the causal-order interpretation is equally clear (causal structure forbids negative-spectral-weight modes from materializing). The challenge is purely technical: connecting the discrete/combinatorial causal-set formalism to the continuum/analytic diagrammatic formalism at loop level.
