+[VERIFIED] The desired source-pair bookkeeping inherited from the prior exact object is
+
+```text
+D1 = {(3,4)},
+D2 = {(1,1)},
+D3 = {(1,1), (2,3)},
+D4 = {(1,3)},
+D5 = {(4,4)}.
+```
+
