+| Precursor leakage witness | `Leak_trig(t) := Σ_{j=3}^5 (|Fj^int-leak(t)| + |Fj^ext-leak(t)|)` | exact amplitude-level leakage ledger |
+| Back-reaction witness | `BR_trig(t) := |F1^back(t)| + |F1^int-leak(t)| + |F1^ext-leak(t)|` | exact amplitude-level carrier feedback ledger |
+| Threshold / delay condition | there exists `t_*` with `T_pre(t) <= η_act` for `t < t_*`, and `V_amp(t), V_out(t) >= λ` on `[t_*, t_* + Δ_delay]` | user-chosen admissibility rule on exact observables |
+
+[CHECKED] The exact desired pieces named above are:
